page_title: 'Using your data with Azure OpenAI securely'
page_description: Use this article to learn about securely using your data for text generation in Azure OpenAI.
chunk_content: Create resource groupCreate a resource group, so you can organize all the relevant resources. The resources in the resource group include but are not limited to:* One Virtual network* Three key services: one Azure OpenAI, one Azure AI Search, one Storage Account* Three Private endpoints, each is linked to one key service* Three Network interfaces, each is associated with one private endpoint* One Virtual network gateway, for the access from on-premises client machines* One Web App with virtual network integrated* One Private DNS zone, so the Web App finds the IP of your Azure OpenAI
